        "body": "<p>You can easily change your recurring gift to FCA through the myFCA Donor Login. Follow these instructions to learn how.</p>\n<p>First, visit <a href=\"https://my.fca.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">my.fca.org</a> and click the \"Manage My Donation\" link in the upper right-hand corner:</p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid black; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpcenter.fca.org/Public%20Help%20Center/myFCA/Donor%20Login/How%20to%20Change%20your%20Recurring%20Gift%20on%20myFCA/image-1.png\" width=\"100%\"></p>\n<p>On the next page, enter the email <span>address you've used </span><span>when making your donations and click the \"Get Login Link\" button:</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid black; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpcenter.fca.org/Public%20Help%20Center/myFCA/Donor%20Login/How%20to%20Change%20your%20Recurring%20Gift%20on%20myFCA/image-2.png\" width=\"100%\"></p>\n<p>You should then receive an email at that address with a special link to log in to your myFCA account. Simply click the link (the \"Login\" button) in that email to proceed:</p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid black; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpcenter.fca.org/Public%20Help%20Center/myFCA/Donor%20Login/How%20to%20Change%20your%20Recurring%20Gift%20on%20myFCA/image-3.png\" width=\"100%\"></p>\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid #4FBFDF; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 5px solid #4FBFDF; background: #E2F4F9; padding: 15px;\">\n<h2 id=\"h_01HA55EFC7A7FZDRA3TGREZ2WN\"><strong><em class=\"fas fa-info-circle\"> </em>FYI</strong></h2>\n<p>If none of your email addresses are recognized, contact FCA Support Services at 1-800-289-0909 and they can help you reset the email address associated with your account.</p>\n</div>\n<p>Once you're logged in, you'll see your myFCA account with information about your gift(s):</p>\n<p style=\"padding: 0 -20px 0 -20px;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid black; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpcenter.fca.org/Public%20Help%20Center/myFCA/Donor%20Login/How%20to%20Change%20your%20Recurring%20Gift%20on%20myFCA/gif-1.gif\" width=\"100%\"></p>\n<p>To edit a gift, simply click the adjacent gear icon ( <em class=\"fa-thin fa-gear\"> </em>):</p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid black; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpcenter.fca.org/Public%20Help%20Center/myFCA/Donor%20Login/How%20to%20Change%20your%20Recurring%20Gift%20on%20myFCA/image-4.png\" width=\"100%\"></p>\n<p>Then on the next page, click \"Edit Payment Details\":</p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid black; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpcenter.fca.org/Public%20Help%20Center/myFCA/Donor%20Login/How%20to%20Change%20your%20Recurring%20Gift%20on%20myFCA/image-5.png\" width=\"100%\"></p>\n<p>In the \"Edit payment details\" pop-up window, you can make changes to your gift. You can change the \"<span style=\"background-color: #fff000;\">Donation amount</span>,\" you can opt to \"<span style=\"background-color: #f7ac08;\">Cover transaction costs</span>,\" the gift \"<span style=\"background-color: #00ffcc;\">Frequency</span>,\" the timing of the <span style=\"background-color: #bb44ff;\">next installment</span>, you can opt to \"<span style=\"background-color: #ff5b5b;\">Make an extra installment now</span>,\" and the \"<span style=\"background-color: #ff2dc6;\">Payment method</span>\":</p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 1px solid black; border-radius: 5px;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpcenter.fca.org/Public%20Help%20Center/myFCA/Donor%20Login/How%20to%20Change%20your%20Recurring%20Gift%20on%20myFCA/image-6.png\" width=\"75%\"></p>\n<p>After making any changes, simply click the \"Confirm\" button. <mark>Your changes will be active immediately!</mark></p>"
    }],
